FBIS4-64487 "drweu086_i_94004" FBIS-WEU-94-086 Daily Report 4 May 1994 FRANCE Japan's Hata Arrives for Talks With Leaders Japan's Hata Arrives for Talks With Leaders OW0405101194 Tokyo KYODO in English 1003 GMT 4 May 94 OW0405101194 Tokyo KYODO English BFN [Text] Paris, May 4 KYODO -- Japanese Prime Minister Tsutomu Hata arrived in Paris shortly before noon Wednesday [4 May] from Rome for talks with French leaders on bilateral and international relations and the July 8-10 Naples economic summit. Hata is scheduled to meet with French President Francois Mitterrand, Prime Minister Edouard Balladur and Paris Mayor Jacques Chirac before flying to Germany on Thursday. Hata will also visit Belgium before returning to Tokyo.
